      • add3WXfr

        Aclf3WBranch add3WXfr(Aclf3WBranch branch,
                      java.lang.String fromBusId,
                      java.lang.String toBusId,
                      java.lang.String tertBusId)
               throws InterpssException
        Add the branch object into the network container and connect to the from bus and to bus identified by the Id(s). For a ground branch, set toBusId=null. The branch id and circuit number may be changed, if parallel branches are allowed. If parallel branches are not allowed and a duplication is found, throws ElementDuplicationException. Also an ElementNotFoundException may be thrown, if the form bus and/or to bus is not found.
        Parameters:
        branch - the branch object to be added
        fromBusId - from bus id
        toBusId - to bus id
        tertBusId - tertiarary bus id
        Throws:
        InterpssException
